➜河南诗人樊国文：诗二首
http://www.sohu.com/a/426818324_100115135	37788
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗二首</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/樊国文</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201023/26a386ba69524544b94fd61dc1c65c9b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七律•国庆（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">国庆中秋喜遇逢，天南海北共欢腾。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">月圆花好歌如意，玉映珠联颂太平。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">愉快观光心暖暖，温馨聚会谊融融。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">辛勤奋斗前程妙，舞乐抒发赞美情。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2020年10月1日于南阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201023/777fa7047b0646ab93c87f4f534ad044.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七律•醉秋（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">日暖风柔胜似春，中秋美景醉游人。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
