➜彩虹：冷默的秋
http://www.sohu.com/a/426819041_100115135	37986
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201023/d87dfd7b050e40a1b072db3d1e61449b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>冷默的秋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/彩虹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天，似乎很凉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">凉的直抽筋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">广场，公园，拐角空地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">许多人，抖擞着精神</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">跳舞，打羽毛球，练</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">太极拳</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>凉，一扫而空</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>脸，满面春风，热情火辣心跳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>悠哉，悠哉，哉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>狂热如一缕红红的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>火焰</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>冒出来，炸开来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一丝丝红，像一个个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>花瓣</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>坠落在亭旁，公园里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">笑，于是荡开了</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
